comments: Trent Jr. (TOR) is established in Tate's (HOU) path and Tate makes marginal contact with Trent Jr. during the screen attempt.
Watanabe (TOR) is established in Christopher's (HOU) path and makes marginal contact during the screen attempt.
Christopher (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during Siakam's (TOR) drive to the basket and makes marginal contact with Siakam's non-shooting arm during the shot attempt.
Trent Jr. (TOR) moves laterally into Green (HOU) and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Sengun (HOU) makes marginal contact with Barnes (TOR) as he disengages to contest the shot attempt.
Sengun (HOU) makes incidental contact with Young's (TOR) arm after his shot attempt at the rim.
Siakam (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Sengun (HOU).
Sengun (HOU) places his off-arm against Siakam (TOR) without extending as he slows his momentum on the perimeter.
Young (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Tate (HOU).
Green (HOU) makes marginal body contact with Trent Jr. (TOR) during his drive towards the rim.
Sengun (HOU) maintains a legal vertical position while contesting Trent Jr.'s (TOR) driving shot attempt.
Sengun (HOU) briefly grasps Siakam's (TOR) arm during the drive to the basket.
Siakam (TOR) briefly places an arm on Sengun's (HOU) back but the marginal contact does not affect his ability to attempt the shot at the basket.
